	The main goal on this project was to know what is the percentage of native trees vs exotic trees (not from Brazil) used in the city's urban forestry to better understand, if and how native trees are taken into consideration when planting and planning the urban forestry.

	I donwloaded the data from the city hall website and imported to the SQL Server:https://www.sigeo.niteroi.rj.gov.br/datasets/0bd714fd0cf8448d986e1fdad0a17d75_0/explore?location=-51.210950%2C-37.500000%2C3

	